cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with improving the sample-efficiency of deep reinforcement learning through the use of experience replay. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics) as it focuses on RL in the context of robotic manipulation tasks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it deals with control of robotic systems, and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the tasks involve visual perception.
